    "description": "ClickHouse replication health: replica queue, absolute delay, readonly replicas, fetches and sends. Degrades to no-data on single-node deployments without Replicated tables. Panels adapted as a reference from the ClickHouse mix-in (Grafana dashboard 23415, github.com/ClickHouse/clickhouse-mixin, commit c54f56e0). Rebuilt on PMM's Apache-2.0 dashboard shell.",
